<div class="data-driven-title fbcms_article_title">Keep Up the Remote Learning!</div>
                <div class="fbcms_article_summary">
<p><sup>All District 215 school buildings will be closed for the remainder of the 2019-2020 school year. <strong>Remote Learning continues every day!</strong> <a href="http://tfd215.org/e-learning-attendance" target="_blank">C</a></sup><a href="http://tfd215.org/e-learning-attendance" target="_blank">heck in here</a> for attendance or use the REMOTE LEARNING tab (in the top left of web version or Menu <img alt="" src="/downloads/north_high_school/menu_lines_1.jpg" style="height:25px; width:30px">  in the top right of mobile device).</p>

<p> </p>

<p>You can access the District 215 Remote Learning Plan and answers to Frequently Asked Questions; all attached to this alert.</p>

<p> </p>

<p>Grab-and-Go Meals are available. <a href="https://www.tfd215.org/downloads/northhome/tfec_joint_statement_03-22-20__1.pdf" target="_blank">Please see this link</a>.</p>

<p> </p>
